{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/2024-08-27-how-to-add-text-below-image-in-react-js/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aHoisting! To add text below image in react js, You can display text below the image by placing  tag and  tag inside div element. It‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aHoisting!</p>\n<p>To add text below image in react js, You can display text below the image by placing <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img/></code> tag and <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;p></code> tag inside div element. It will add text below image in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to add text below image in react js.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import react component.</li>\n<li>Create a Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start with the first step.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Install and create a new React app.</h3>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Import react component.</h3>\n<p>After installing, you have to import your React component.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> myImage <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./light.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Create a Component.</h3>\n<p>You can use <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img src={myImage} alt=\"image\" style={{ width: '100vh' }}/></code> to add text below image in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>img src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>myImage<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"image\"</span> style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">width</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'100vh'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>This is the text below the image<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Add text below image example.</h3>\n<p>The below code is an example of a React. You have to import <code class=\"language-text\">'./light.jpg'</code> and set <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img src={myImage} alt=\"image\" style={{ width: '100vh' }}/></code> and <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;p></code> tag to add text below image in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  \n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> myImage <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./light.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>img src<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>myImage<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> alt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"image\"</span> style<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">width</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'100vh'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>This is the text below the image<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;p></code> tag to add text below image in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4a9783ff86cff1e266a80a2612aca954/ec897/text-below.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.67088607594937%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRloAAABXRUJQVlA4IE4AAABQAwCdASoUAAkAPtFWo0uoJKMhsAgBABoJYwAAXGlCyQFAAAD+zQgaAvVmvNnexr948N72przgzykiiG/yB9C/w+E080/BVTOFJg0AAAA='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, add, text, below, image\"\n        title=\"React, add, text, below, image\"\n        src=\"/static/4a9783ff86cff1e266a80a2612aca954/8aab1/text-below.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4a9783ff86cff1e266a80a2612aca954/81b7c/text-below.webp 158w,\n/static/4a9783ff86cff1e266a80a2612aca954/6ea66/text-below.webp 315w,\n/static/4a9783ff86cff1e266a80a2612aca954/8aab1/text-below.webp 630w,\n/static/4a9783ff86cff1e266a80a2612aca954/a70f5/text-below.webp 945w,\n/static/4a9783ff86cff1e266a80a2612aca954/4ef06/text-below.webp 1260w,\n/static/4a9783ff86cff1e266a80a2612aca954/ec897/text-below.webp 1366w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to add text below image in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"August 27, 2024","description":"Example of add text below image in react js with step by step tutorial - aHoisting","social_image":{"absolutePath":"/Users/mac/Documents/hoisting/ahoisting/static/media/template/reactjs.jpg"}}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to add text beside image in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-08-27-how-to-add-text-beside-image-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to add rupee symbol in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2024-08-26-how-to-add-rupee-symbol-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2024-08-27-how-to-add-text-below-image-in-react-js/","prevSlug":"/blog/2024-08-27-how-to-add-text-beside-image-in-react-js/","nextSlug":"/blog/2024-08-26-how-to-add-rupee-symbol-in-react-js/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2555585279","2714594843","3159585216"]}